FBIS4-28882 "dreas114_c_94031" FBIS-EAS-94-114 Daily Report 3 Jun 1994 North Korea Declaration Supported by Canadian Party Declaration Supported by Canadian Party SK0306214094 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1506 GMT 3 Jun 94 SK0306214094 Pyongyang KCNA English BFN [Text] Pyongyang, June 3 (KCNA) -- The National Committee of the Quebec Communist Party of Canada recently adopted a resolution supporting the Pyongyang declaration "Let us defend and advance the cause of socialism." The resolution denounced the U.S. imperialists and the South Korean authorities' provocative acts of constantly threatening peace on the Korean peninsula. Condemning the large-scale campaign against the DPRK over its "nuclear issue" as a move to destabilize the socialist Korea, the resolution expressed solidarity with the Korean people in their struggle for defence of socialism.
